  the MIT License. See `docs/lfs-git/appendices/license.xml` and
  `docs/blfs-git/appendices/creat-comm.xml` for the full text.
* **GLFS Book** – Creative Commons Attribution-NonCommercial-ShareAlike 2.0
  with the MIT License applying to build instructions. See
  `docs/glfs/appendices/creat-comm.xml` and `docs/glfs/appendices/mit-lic.xml`.
* **JHALFS** – MIT License. See `docs/jhalfs/LICENSE`.
* **JHALFS menu configuration system** – ISC License. See
  `docs/jhalfs/menu/LICENSE.txt`.

When redistributing the documentation or any derived materials, please ensure
that the appropriate license notices from the above files accompany those
works.
